  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 15,000 \u0bae\u0bc6.\u0ba4\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd. - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Resolution to distribute 15,000 MT of fertilizer for tea cultivation. - Minister of Agriculture",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Agriculture and Wildlife Conservation Minister Mahinda Amaraweera said that out of 40,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer made available under the Indian loan program, 15,000 metric tons of urea fertilizer has been decided to be given to tea cultivation.",
        "He mentioned the above during the discussion held with the officials of the Ministry of Agriculture regarding the supply of fertilizers required for mass agriculture and the supply of fuel for agricultural activities.",
        "Out of the 65,000 metric tons of fertilizer to be made available under the Indian loan program, 40,000 metric tons of fertilizer have been made available in the first phase. Currently, 60 percent of the fertilizer distribution is complete with the aim of mass agriculture.",
        "The mixed fertilizer required for vegetable production will be produced and distributed to the market within two weeks. Out of the imported fertilizer, 15,000 metric tons of fertilizer has been decided to be distributed to tea cultivation, the minister told the officials."
      ],
